## Key Insights
1. max_steps = 10000 in tournament (not 5000)
2. Economy sustainability is critical for second half
3. num_agents bug helps large teams (more alignment pressure)
4. Small teams need guaranteed miners (economy collapses otherwise)
5. Scrambling is essential (SustainV3 without scrambling scored 2.77)
6. AdaptiveTeam combines best of both worlds

